Failing to validate input and prevent injection attacks - Lazy Cat
Ignoring updates to third-party dependencies - Clueless Koala
Storing passwords in plain text - Password Potato
Hardcoding sensitive information into code - Forgetful Fish
Neglecting to test applications for vulnerabilities - Distracted Duck
Disabling security features because they're "too much work" - Reckless Rabbit
Ignoring security event logging and anomaly monitoring - Jumpy Jellyfish
Failing to encrypt sensitive data in transit and at rest - Silly Seal
Failing to enable two-factor authentication - Sleepy Sloth
Failing to limit access to sensitive information - Curious Cat
